                <li><a href="http://rules.ssw.com.au/Communication/RulesToBetterEmail/Pages/EmailToMyself.aspx">Do you send
                    yourself emails?</a></li>
                <li><a href="/ssw/Standards/Rules/RulestoBetterInstantMessenger.aspx#ImportantChatsEmail">
                    Do you confirm important IM chats by email</a></li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                Email, Instant Messenger and (confirmed) verbal agreements are utilized extensively
                during a project where newly discovered work, delays, or other work outside the
                initial scope is required. SSW may use <a href="/SSW/ExtremeEmails">Extreme Emails</a>
                to manage this process.
            </p>
