            <li>
                <h2>Do you ensure an excellent 1st date? (aka Winning customers with a "Specification Review")</h2><a name="first-date"></a>
                <p>So you had a good <a href="">initial meeting</a> (like a 1st coffee with a new girl), and you have agreed to have 
