                <p> For the majority of new clients, a <a href="http://rules.ssw.com.au/Management/RulesToBetterProjectManagement/Pages/SpecificationReview.aspx">
                    Specification Review</a> (also known as a Spec Review) will be your 1st paid engagement with them. This is to work out the requirements, 
